main event: Two fish-shaped objects were sighted close to each other, one appearing as a half circle behind the other, and then they suddenly faded.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for about 1 minute,Two objects were reported as being fish-shaped,One object was reported to be half a mile behind the other,The observer concluded that the objects might be aircraft flying in trail formation,There were at least three previous sightings of similar objects by six or more different individuals from the same post.
witness description: GOC personnel of the same post
